frames.caption: A lone figure wearing a traditional conical hat sits in a small wooden boat, drifting on a calm, mist-covered lake. Towering karst mountains rise in the background, partially obscured by the thick fog, creating a serene and mystical atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene depicts a tranquil setting on a misty lake surrounded by dramatic karst mountains. The fog adds a layer of mystery, while the solitary boat and figure evoke a sense of peaceful solitude.

frames.caption: A lone figure wearing a traditional conical hat navigates a small boat through a misty river. The serene landscape is dominated by towering karst mountains partially shrouded in fog. Traditional wooden houses line the riverbank, adding to the tranquil atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene captures a peaceful river setting enveloped in mist, with a solitary person in a boat. The backdrop features dramatic karst mountains and traditional architecture, creating a harmonious blend of nature and human presence.
